run-*.bat/sh
------------
- these go into /usr/bin/ on UNIX
- they stay here on Windows
- they call the actual stuff in whatever way is appropriate

gnumed-archiv.conf
------------------
- this goes into /etc/gnumed/ and optionally ~/gnumed/ on UNIX
- stays here on Windows
- this is handed over by the run-()ers via command line

*.py
----
- these go into /usr/share/gnumedarchiv/ on UNIX
- they stay here on Windows

*.mo
----
- these go into /usr/share/locale/LC_MESSAGES/de_DE/ on UNIX
- they stay here on Windows
